↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstDEfhu","text_ar":"استضعفهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he found him to be so;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he asserted him to be"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaEalahu","text_ar":"جَعَلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) or, as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tDE~fhu","text_ar":"تضعّفهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"esteemed him to be so, and therefore"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"behaved proudly, haughtily,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"insolently, towards him, in respect of worldly things, because of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"poverty, and meanness of condition."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAth, TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galabaniY A^aholu Alkuwfapi A^asotaEomilu Ealayohimu Almuw^omina fayuDaE~afu","text_ar":"غَلَبَنِى اَهْلُ الكُوفَةِ اَسْتَعْمِلُ عَلَيْهِمُ المُوْمِنَ فَيُضَعَّفُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA^asotaEomilu Ealayohimu AlqawiY~a fayufaj~aru","text_ar":"وَاَسْتَعْمِلُ عَلَيْهِمُ القَوِىَّ فَيُفَجَّرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The people of El-Koofeh have overcome me: I employ as governor over them the believer, and he is esteemed weak; and I employ as governor over them the strong, and he is charged with unrighteousness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is a saying mentioned in a trad. of 'Omar. (TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He attributed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ascribed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. a man, (O,) or (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. a tradition, [&c.,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaEof","text_ar":"ضَعْف"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weakness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"app., in the case of a man,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of judgment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in the case of a tradition &c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of authority"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O, K, TA.)       -A2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He doubled it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made it double, covering one part of it with another part."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  See also the next paragraph, in two places."}],"source_refs":["S","O","Msb","K"]},{"entry_id":"n25846","headword_ar":"ضَعْفَةٌ","root":"DEf","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Weakness of heart,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"littleness of intel-ligence."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n25847","headword_ar":"ضَعَفَةٌ","root":"DEf","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A party,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"company,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small company,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iro*imapN","text_ar":"شِرْذِمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the Arabs."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  Also a pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaEiyfN","text_ar":"ضَعِيفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (S &c.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}